  "detailed_description": "Smashing time is a VR sandbox simulation that lets you break everything around you.<br />\r\nYou can go rampage in a museum, wreak havoc in the oval office, completely destroy an appartment, or a restaurant.<br />\r\nClimb on the wall, break the roof, pee on things, burn everything down, or tag the walls, just choose the way you want to smash it down !",
